mbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191128%2Flarge%2F1574952027_4d30.png&h=f92b1784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191128/large/1574952106_6d14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191128%2Flarge%2F1574952106_6d14.png&h=8ef84ef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191128/large/1574952624_1d9c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191128%2Flarge%2F1574952624_1d9c.png&h=59cb7d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191129/60321910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191129%2F60321910&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLR4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=486deb62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191129%2F60321910&h=686d2b85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191129/60321910</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T00:50:27.000Z","msg":"講事實咋喎！屌！CLS<br />\n要指鹿為馬？"},{"pid":"5afffca206a591f79f17e9d931c1aec789ea2ad3","tid":1761286,"uid":201356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4baf2309c4335eed452b9a5c8cda05d60c717eab","tid":1761286,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T22:12:27.000Z","msg":"有小學因工作紙因讚揚美國河流較中國河流潔淨，並提及中國水污染問題，遭中共官媒炮轟「崇洋眨（貶）中」。涉事學校前日（27日）發聲明，稱出卷老師僅一時疏忽，當中不涉政治考量，對引起外界誤會深感抱歉，將更正並重發有關工作紙。<br />\n<br />\n早前有網民在網上發佈一份沙田培基小學的小二英文工作紙，內文分別提及位於美國黃石國家公園及中國的河流。內文以河流作第一人稱書寫，美國河流在文中表示非常高興，因河流獲國人友善對待，水質乾淨清澈，附近亦長滿花草。而中國河流曾叮囑大家不要靠近他，因他不獲國人友善對待，河水亦十分骯髒和且發出臭味，該段結尾亦以河流對世人的求救作結。公開工作紙的網民批評，工作紙是傳播仇視國家訊息，斥涉事教師「別有用心」、「圖為學生洗腦」，要求校方嚴懲。<br />\n<br />\n培基小學昨發聲明表示，校方近年積極推動學生認識中國歷史文化，而因應社會情況，校方早於8月已給予老師清晰指引，必須讓學生以持平客觀態度分析問題和討